snippet.title: RIP Amber Heard Left Heartbroken By Passing Of Beloved One..Fans Sends Prayers
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has just revealed that her mother, Paige Heard, has died.The 'Aquaman' actress announced the heartbreaking news on Instagram sharing several photos of herself with her mother. In the post, Heard also shared a message about the untimely death.
"I am heartbroken and devastated beyond belief at the loss of my mom, Paige Heard. She left us too early, clasping onto the memory of her beautiful, gentle soul. She will be missed from the very depths of our hearts forever," the actress began.
